Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 禾斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗之霧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗之風呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗又再度支配了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 美茹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個戒指會保護妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緩和了墮落時的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像要想起甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人到底想去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五最終話  [ 輝煌之後 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個景像我好像看過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是艾斯托爾的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯…艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有騙妳 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是艾斯托爾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是作夢吧 你是艾斯托爾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影之一族的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有別的路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快找 快找呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪惡的氣在這個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在光之國失去記憶 在那裡流浪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在作夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾 沒想到能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都在祈禱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 莎朗 我好想念妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無所謂 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年來我一直等這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你何時變得這麼勇壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗 我喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快瘋了 再插 再插
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 你是何時變得這麼厲害的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 艾斯托爾 我還要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾 我快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾 讓我們一起…拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣太難看了 禾斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲到此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺死你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把 Words Worth 石板敲得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們無法再重組
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的統治者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也來嚐嚐那個女人的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是地下城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在20年前的戰爭中失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才注意到我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了追尋你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都來這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去見大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓓爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我不會再繞遠路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是蓓爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是卻不是平時的蓓爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 普陸斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪惡的黑暗撤離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mistral Wind！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾\N普陸斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾…\N普陸斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美茹 莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在那裡做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓓爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做甚麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管那個 各位 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達西奧跟光之國的參謀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要毀滅光與影之國…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人應該是想破壞石板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界陷入黑暗的邪惡元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓓爾妲 帶我們去找那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法布利陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面有類似通風口的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攪不好能通往城內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快通知全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣攻進他們根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女人真緊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要製造光與影的混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把裡面的種子都挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有女人聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是夢 我馬上救妳下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩人認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且似乎還有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾大人 我好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱得這麼緊耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗雅 他是妳的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mis…Mistral…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險 有大水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓光與影互相為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們預計的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫使我們不得不提早計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口…不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑你的身體 你做得出甚麼來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 Words Worth 石板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你們影之一族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這個妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們才是破壞石板的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影的國王聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你們一起殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mistral Wind！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 居然敢破壞我的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把世界化成死亡世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美茹 把妳的力量賜給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗之風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到我本來是光之國的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾大人的年紀應該更老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你戴的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我們一樣的時光送給了艾斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了製造光與影的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把光之一族的小孩搶來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我太想知道石板的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾的父親是不是普陸斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人的臉龐與劍招跟普陸斯一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上普陸斯突然消失的謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的 一切都吻合了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是早點注意到黑暗的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就能省去無意義的戰爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無意義的戰爭啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個可以給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石板上的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面寫甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒看過這種文字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影一族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 這女孩就是光與影的混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傾聽我的話吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到 我們會輸給一個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:24:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是禾斯卡沒有搶來光之一族的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企圖讀懂石板的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.03,0:24:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們差一點就達到目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.54,0:24:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體在消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們製造光明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也製造了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那不是你們最後的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.06,0:24:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看藍色的屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.90,0:24:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將來有天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們會成為完整的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說) 第五最終話完  全劇完
